				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				Oh one thing I forgot to mention,<BR>
<BR>
I'm told that CHA affects the radius of control over your pet. I never noticed it, but all of my pet users have been either Iksar or DE and both have low cha so that's not surprising. Anyway, if this is true, then that would be a good argument for using High Elf, as they have the highest CHA. <BR>
<BR>
Again, in the end, stats aren't going to have huge affects, and eventually they will all get balanced by items and the softcap anyway - I honestly think other considerations, such as looks, team if you're on a team pvp server, special abilities, faction, etc. are more important considerations - which ones are most important are a personal matter, but it's important to have a character that fits your style first and foremost. <BR>
